Entries.default: "We shall return with the sacred torc, bathor."
"Keep pace if you are able, kith."
"The defiler has turned even our own beasts against us."
"The priestess and the torc await within."
"Take care that you do not stride into the lava."
"Retrieve the torc, kith. You have earned this honor."
"Bathor, we return victorious! By means of a kith, no less!"
"God or not, the defiler will die for this."
"Do you yet live, kith? Ah, good."
"May Magran feast on your soul, you traitorous creature!"
"I must report this to the bathor, at once."
"I will end your treacherous existence, kith!"
